examples.en: The poles were placed wide apart.

examples.en: The Earth rotates on an axis between the north and south poles.

examples.en: Both are brilliant pianists, though they're poles apart in style.

examples.en: Washington and Beijing are at opposite poles (=think in two completely different ways) on this issue.

examples.en: I suppose in every atom two poles in its superficies, and a Central point within its substance, which I call its Bias.
